=== Drug-Drug Interactions as Probes
  <sec:drug-drug-interactions>

*Certainty: 0.15.* Drug-drug interaction logic as a diagnostic tool is entirely inferential. No ME/CFS study has used drug combinations as formal diagnostic probes. Risk of adverse interactions is real; combinations discussed below assume physician supervision and sequential introduction with monitoring.

